We will fight hard tomorrow against team SA and your support will make us stronger. Share your wishes for Team India with #ChaseTheRecord.

Happy Birthday, Papa.
We miss you every single day.
Your strength, your love, your fight—those are the things that guide us.
You never gave up, and we carry that will with us.
Hardik and I can only hope to be the kind of father you were: strong, kind, and always present.
Your legacy lives on in everything we do. ❤️
